cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Algorithm OF 1032: An Adaptive Multi-Policy Search Framework for Efficient Searching in Sorted Arrays"

message: >
  If you use this repository or Algorithm OF 1032 in your research,
  please cite it using the metadata below.

