version: "6.0"

date-released: "2026-07-06"

abstract: >
  Algorithm OF 1032 is an adaptive multi-policy search framework for
  sorted arrays. The framework estimates the relative position of a
  target element and dynamically selects one of multiple specialized
  search policies through a centralized Policy Manager. The framework
  integrates the Relative Position Estimator (RPE), Policy Manager (PM),
  Binary Search Engine (BSE), Head-Oriented Search Policy (HOP), and
  Tail-Oriented Search Policy (TOP).

